  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nWe would like to upload certain historical states, weak subjectivity states, to the cloud, for use in bootstrapping sync.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nWe need to expand our debug/states API endpoint to be able to serve historical checkpoint states at weak subjectivity epochs.\r\nCurrently, the endpoint just checks our state cache, 404s if the requested state is not found.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\nSee https://notes.ethereum.org/@adiasg/weak-subjectvity-eth2#Weak-Subjectivity-Checkpoint\r\n",
